      "link": "11",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "26": {
          "id": "26",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I was preoccupied defeating Ketheric Thorm.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "11",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "40": {
              "id": "40",
              "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
              "text": "Who? Oh - right. Well, forget about that magungus. We have more important things to worry about. Like Wulbren.",
              "context": "NodeContext: 'muh-GUN-guss' (hard g's).",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "11",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Barcus, Wulbren wants nothing to do with you. He made that clear.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [
                    "HAV_WrootRequest_State_ReunionDone"
                  ],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "11",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "33": {
                      "id": "33",
                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                      "text": "Oh, forget about that. Wulbren and the Ironhand Gnomes are planning something dreadful in the city.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "11",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "36": {
                  "id": "36",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "If I have to hear the name 'Wulbren' one more time...",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "14",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "22": {
                      "id": "22",
                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                      "text": "You'll what? Tie me to a windmill? Enslave me in the Underdark? Smack me upside the head? I assure you, circumstance has beaten you to it.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "45": {
                          "id": "45",
                          "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                          "text": "But it doesn't do to remain smack\u00e8d. We fall, we moan, then we rise to annoy our enemies once more.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "14",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "3": {
                  "id": "3",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What about him?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "14": {
                      "id": "14",
                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                      "text": "Wulbren and the Ironhand Gnomes are planning something dreadful in the city.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "20",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "11": {
                          "id": "11",
                          "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                          "text": "They have runepowder. They have motive. We have to stop them.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "20",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "24": {
                              "id": "24",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "It seems we'll have our hands full in Baldur's Gate.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "20",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "9": {
                                  "id": "9",
                                  "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                  "text": "With the sword of justice in one hand and the shield of self-righteousness in the other, we most certainly will.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "20": {
                                      "id": "20",
                                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                      "text": "To saving the city - and my fool of a friend.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "25": {
                              "id": "25",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Leave it to me, Barcus. You've proven you aren't able for this kind of thing.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "20",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "29": {
                                  "id": "29",
                                  "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                  "text": "Knowing when to ask for help is a sign of wisdom, not weakness.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "20",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "49": {
                                      "id": "49",
                                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                      "text": "You helped me in this gods-awful quagmire; when we're back in the city, I'll be fully in my element once more.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "20",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "31": {
                              "id": "31",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Is this just because Wulbren rejected you?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "HAV_WrootRequest_State_ReunionDone"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "20",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "0": {
                                  "id": "0",
                                  "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                  "text": "I'll not deny he wounded me. I cared for Wulbren - care for him, really. But he's... well, he's acting like a true idiot.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "16": {
                                      "id": "16",
                                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                      "text": "It isn't the first time, and I'm sure it won't be the last. But I won't let him hurt anyone - or himself.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "28": {
                              "id": "28",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "How can you be sure?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "20",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "7": {
                                  "id": "7",
                                  "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                  "text": "Because they're a gaggle of vindictive crybabies with no sense of propriety.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "2": {
                                      "id": "2",
                                      "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                      "text": "That is to say, they gabbed about their plans like geese, and I overheard them, like a very devious goose.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "32": {
                              "id": "32",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "The city has more important concerns than a bunch of gnomes with a grudge.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "20",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "48": {
                                  "id": "48",
                                  "speaker": "Barcus Wroot",
                                  "text": "You're tired from your exertions. Who could blame you? Have a smoke, a wash, and a cup of tea, and let's regroup when you're more yourself.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "20",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
